headline: DTE Energy and NextCycle Michigan team up to spark fresh ideas in recycling
summary: As part of its ongoing history as a driver of innovation and steward of the environment, DTE Energy has partnered with NextCycle Michigan to sponsor a pitch competition to find smart, creative ways to reuse materials like wood chips and wind turbine blades and help push the energy industry toward a more sustainable future.
